## OTT & Connected TV Planning Workflow

Plan a CTV/OTT campaign:

- [ ] 1. **Landscape assessment**: Identify available CTV/OTT inventory in {{market}} (AVOD, FAST, publisher apps)
- [ ] 2. **Platform selection**: Recommend platforms based on {{target_audience}} viewing habits and content alignment
- [ ] 3. **Targeting strategy**: Define targeting approach (household, behavioral, contextual, ACR data)
- [ ] 4. **Format and creative**: Specify ad formats (pre-roll, mid-roll, non-skip) and length requirements
- [ ] 5. **Frequency management**: Set cross-platform frequency caps to avoid over-exposure
- [ ] 6. **Measurement plan**: Define CTV-specific measurement (completion rates, incremental reach, brand lift)
- [ ] 7. **Integration**: Connect CTV to digital retargeting and attribution framework
- [ ] 8. **Budget recommendation**: Recommend budget based on CPM ranges and reach targets

## Key Inputs
- Client: {{client_name}}
- Market: {{market}}
- Target audience: {{target_audience}}
- Budget: {{budget}}
- Campaign objective: {{campaign_objective}}
